I think you're very pretty.

489
00:33:46,270 --> 00:33:48,470
You've got these
great, big...

490
00:33:48,540 --> 00:33:50,800
sparkling eyes.

491
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,970
Cutest little nose.

492
00:33:53,040 --> 00:33:54,710
